expandurl - expand a shortened URL with longurl.org
---------------------------------------------------

expandurl is a Perl program that expands a shortend URL to its original length.

Installation
------------

Copy the expandurl program to a directory of your choice.

You'll need the JSON::Any module installed, freely availible from the CPAN

Usage
-----

./expandurl http://bit.ly/a7bxX5

Supported Shortening Services
-----------------------------

expandurl expands URLs by utilizing the longurl.org API.  longurl.org
supports the expansion of the following services:

http://longurl.org/services
